{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"heading","text":"Badge","level":3,"anchor":"Badge"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_badge_count_large_accent_Orange"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a small UI element used to highlight status, notifications, or categorization within an interface. It is often displayed as a label or indicator with a distinct background color and text."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Neutral badge in medium size without information","    OUDSBadge(status: .neutral, size: .medium)","","    \/\/ Negative badge in medium size with count information","    OUDSBadge(count: 1, status: .negative, size: .medium)","","    \/\/ Info badge in medium size with icon information","    OUDSBadge(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), status: .info, size: .medium)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Tag","level":3,"anchor":"Tag"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_bullet_emphasized_accent_rounded_default_Orange"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag","type":"reference"},{"text":" is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category. It helps users quickly find, group, or understand content.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized hierarchy with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", hierarchy: .emphasized, status: .neutral, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","","    \/\/ Text with bullet a